# West Harbour Borough Empowering Act 1884Local Act1884 No 22

Date of assent6 November 1884

## Contents

[Title][0]

[1][1] [Short Title][1]

[2][2] [West Harbour Borough may borrow $2,101.75c to pay debt to Waikouaiti County][2]

